node.text: Librarian Zooey at your service! So proud to be on the ground with @Baby2Baby at their Back2School event this week. Thank you @epic4kids for helping make this week possible and putting so many smiles on the Baby2Baby kids' faces with your back to school library.  My heart is so full after helping distribute books, backpacks, school supplies, and many more basic essentials to the children Baby2Baby serves to get ready for the school year ahead. Follow @baby2baby to learn how you can support! 💗
